{"tid":321424,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"唱歌技術一問","createTime":"2017-07-14T08:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T05:17:03.000Z","uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e01e458df35099eb3b69fe51b308bd0644a0af","tid":321424,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打清唱就好好聽<br />\n一跟旋律就甩晒<br />\n例如上完高音之後落唔番低音<br />\n但清唱又唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43a93eecf3e48c7936184cfb5ae1563b817914d","tid":321424,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"唔識唱歌，但跟音樂唱個呼吸節奏係俾音樂帶住<br />\n清唱可以自己控制<br />\n變相咪要練到自己配合到音樂先得"},{"pid":"6d8ae4ff1ab3bdc4ed5e1d6e322dddb0adeac63b","tid":321424,"uid":10335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"巴打嘅意思係上完高音之後會落唔準定係完全落唔返嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be24a1e1f0003f21aab01e681729ed3b23d3c1f","tid":321424,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"姐係你個拍子差 <br />\n所以先會甩beat<br />\n<br />\n搞到拍子同諗點樣可以唱好d"},{"pid":"a174d99bd0deea41671243974acfd7abc292fb9f","tid":321424,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:53:58.000Z","msg":"錄嚟聽下先講 <br />\n有時清唱你以為自己唱啱音<br />\n其實低左個key 搞到真唱個陣唱錯哂"},{"pid":"cd32e20be81e710e69ddf422d6759857fc2046ea","tid":321424,"uid":51205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"你確定你清唱係好聽？"},{"pid":"b5e7a988a4fdad956a3ec58e822a1351710633de","tid":321424,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識唱歌，但跟音樂唱個呼吸節奏係俾音樂帶住<br />\n清唱可以自己控制<br />\n變相咪要練到自己配合到音樂先得</blockquote><br />\n有比音樂帶住既感覺就得，再勁d可以帶動音樂，唔會比音樂㩒住把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0811fc580d5865b1392c407d2577676f67908476","tid":321424,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"多數係因為你清唱個陣自己定個Key<br />\n<br />\n個Key你自己最擅長最掌握到<br />\n<br />\n但有音樂個陣就唱原Key就唔習慣<br />\n<br />\n加上一轉音你就會想翻去清唱個個key，就搞成咁"},{"pid":"49c048d4d2f0baf4bbfe33dcf0bdb1dd7e382fa7","tid":321424,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多數係因為你清唱個陣自己定個Key<br />\n<br />\n個Key你自己最擅長最掌握到<br />\n<br />\n但有音樂個陣就唱原Key就唔習慣<br />\n<br />\n加上一轉音你就會想翻去清唱個個key，就搞成咁</blockquote><br />\n我覺得都係咁 點練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}